ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition1
ScalarVariable.description: eSST1A.simpleLagLim.state < eSST1A.simpleLagLim.outMin and eSST1A.simpleLagLim.K * eSST1A.imLeadLag1.y - eSST1A.simpleLagLim.state > 0.0

ScalarVariable.name: $whenCondition2
ScalarVariable.description: eSST1A.simpleLagLim.state > eSST1A.simpleLagLim.outMax and eSST1A.simpleLagLim.K * eSST1A.imLeadLag1.y - eSST1A.simpleLagLim.state < 0.0
